# what microsoft 365 copilot is
Microsoft 365 Copilot is a generative AI assistant that is built directly into Microsoft 365 apps like Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Outlook, and Teams.
# what it depends on 
IDENTITY: Copilot uses your Microsoft ID and license to determine which version you can access.
DATA: Copilot data includes files, chats, emails, calendars, and other content connected through Microsoft Graph and relevant to your work.
PERMISSION: Copilot  respects your existing permissions like,  not accessing files you can't see. it relies on the functions of ypur microsoft 365 environment.
Microsoft 365 copilot does not work alone as it is built into microsoft 365 apps. It is not a replacement with human, but is is made to help during workflows.
